            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": "This paper proposes a novel framework, shown in Fig. 1, referred to as the Boosting of Thoughts (BoT), which achieves the *boosting* mechanism that embraces *aggregation* and *experience*, thereby enabling the progressive refinement of unreliable reasoning steps (weak thoughts) by learning from errors to eventually solve various problems. Starting with a simple prompt without human annotations",
